<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5572953>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Chelae, female: A, Anteon abdulnouri Olmi, 1987 (Lebanon – Redrawn from Olmi 1987); B, Anteon pubicorne (Dalman,1818) (Italy – redrawn from Olmi, 1984); C, Bocchus hyalinus Olmi, 1998 (Oman – Redrawn from Olmi 1998); D, Dryinus tamaricicola Rakhshani & Olmi, 2016 (Iran – redrawn from Derafshan et al. 2016). Scale bars: 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5572953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5572985>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. – Bocchus hyalinus Olmi, 1998, female: A, head, lateral view; B, head, frontal view; C, head, dorsal view; D, mesosoma, lateral view; E, mesosoma, dorsal view; F, metapectal-propodeal complex, dorsal view; G, chela. H, habitus, lateral view. Scale bars: A-C, E, F, 300 μm; D, 500 μm; G, 200 μm; H, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5572985/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5572979>
    dc:description "FIG. 9. — Aphelopus orphanidesi Olmi, 1994, female: A, head, frontal view; B, head, dorsal view; C, mesosoma, dorsal view; D, metapectal-propodeal complex, dorsal view; E, fore wing; F, habitus, dorsal view. Scale bars: A-D, 300 μm; E, F, 500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5572979/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5572963>
    dc:description "FIG. 5. — Anteon abdulnouri Olmi, 1987, male: A, head, frontal view; B, head, dorsal view; C, mesosoma, dorsal view; D, metapectal-propodeal complex, dorsal view; E, fore wing; F, habitus, lateral view. Scale bars: A-D, 300 μm; E, F, 500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5572963/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5572975>
    dc:description "FIG. 8. — Aphelopus melaleucus (Dalman, 1818),male:A, head,frontal view; B, head,dorsal view;C, mesosoma,dorsal view; D, metapectal-propodeal complex, dorsal view; E, fore wing; F, habitus, lateral view. Scale bars: A-D, 300 μm; E, F, 500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5572975/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5572981>
    dc:description "FIG. 10. — Aphelopus orphanidesi Olmi, 1994, male: A, head, frontal view; B, head, dorsal view; C, mesosoma, dorsal view; D, metapectal-propodeal complex, dorsal view; E, fore wing; F, habitus, lateral view. Scale bars: A-D, 300 μm; E, F, 500 μm." ;
